front.title: <>Spaceport City
front.gametext: Light:  If you have a non-unique Rebel leader at same or related site, Force drain +1 here. May not be deployed to Bespin, Dagobah, Endor, Hoth, Kashyyyk or Yavin 4.  Dark:  If your thief or scout present, Force drain +1 here. May not be deployed to Bespin, Dagobah, Endor, Hoth, Kashyyyk or Yavin 4.
